OL,4,CCovid jabs not recommended for most
OL,5,C12-15 year olds
OL,6, The UK's vaccine advisory body has
OL,7, refused to give the green light to
OL,8, vaccinating healthy children aged 12-15
OL,9, years on health grounds alone.
OL,11,FThe JCVI said children were at such a
OL,12,Flow risk from the virus that jabs would
OL,13,Foffer only a marginal benefit.
OL,15,FThe UK's four chief medical officers
OL,16,Fhave now been asked to have the final
OL,17,Fsay, and consider the wider impact on
OL,18,Fschools and society.
OL,20,FHealth Secretary Sajid Javid says a
OL,21,Fdecision will be made shortly.
